name: Galina
description:
I am woman with natural beauty: without silicone, glamor and pathos)))But with perfect taste. I try to treat people the same way, that they are treat me. I would love to meet someone who loves the same things as me. Companionship, going out to dinner. Someone who loves to travel but also loves going back home to share the great places you just visited.
I want him to be first of all honest, faithful, kind. I’m looking for
a person I can relay on and share good and bad moments in life. I want
him to be my friend and my beloved at once. Is it you, my dear?
